com.box.boxjavalibv2.filetransfer
Class BoxFileDownload

java.lang.Object
  com.box.boxjavalibv2.filetransfer.BoxFileDownload

public class BoxFileDownload
extends java.lang.Object

Contains logic for downloading a user's file from Box API and supports using IFileTransferListener to monitor downloading progress.
